title: 51: The Costco Haul Episode
itunes:title: The Costco Haul Episode
description: Empty out the trunk — Hungry Girl is going to Costco! In this episode, Lisa and the gang CHEW & TELL over a dozen tasty and healthy food finds from the famous big box store! Everything from fajitas, burgers, sausages, dips, soups, frozen sandwiches, protein bars and SO MUCH MORE! Plus a chocolatey treat that’s only 20 calories per piece and is to die for! Make some room in your fridge, freezer and pantry, your next stop (after you listen to this podcast) is Costco!!! [hungry-girl.com/foodcast](http://hungry-girl.com/foodcast)
